text: Jettingen-Scheppach is a market community in Günzburg Landkreis in the Schwaben (Swabia) Regierungsbezirk in Bavaria. It is between Ulm and Augsburg. Its population as of 1 December 2005 was 7,044. == References == == Other websites == * Jettingen-Scheppach's official website Category:Settlements in Günzburg (district)
